<div class="sidebar-content col-sm-12">
  <h2>About Cambase</h2>
  <p>Cambase.io is a project by Evercam.io in order to make it easier for software developers to have a reliable, up to date source of model hardware information available via a public API.</p>
  <p>We encourage individuals and vendors to contribute more information to Cambase.io as a resource for future developers.</p>
  <p>This data is licensed under creative commons and is freely available for both private and commercial use.</p>
  <div class="sidebar-stats icon-cameras">
    <%= link_to pluralize(Model.all.length, 'Model'), models_path %>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar-stats icon-recorders">
    <%= link_to pluralize(Recorder.all.length, 'Recorder'), recorders_path %>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar-stats icon-manufacturers">
    <%= link_to pluralize(Vendor.all.length, 'Vendor'), vendors_path %>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar-stats icon-images">
    <span><%= pluralize(Image.where(owner_type: "Model").length, 'Image') %></span>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar-stats icon-documents">
    <span><%= pluralize(Document.where(owner_type: "Model").length, 'Document') %></span>
  </div>
</div>
